Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/wildsurfer/vim-ide.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Add new plugin:

    git submodule add git://github.com/altercation/vim-colors-solarized.git bundle/vim-colors-solarize

